1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with real-time data dissemination in wireless sensor networks, which is a networking problem. 
2. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper proposes a scheduling algorithm for data transmissions in a distributed system of sensor nodes. 
3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper discusses packet prioritization and scheduling policies for efficient data dissemination, which are algorithmic problems. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with real-time data dissemination, which is a control problem. 
5. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper proposes a novel algorithm for scheduling data transmissions, which could potentially involve information theory concepts.
